                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_429_r1l6">Glancʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnad wiſſen daʒ vns die
